{"id":25921,"date":"2024-01-08T07:13:00","date_gmt":"2024-01-08T01:43:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=25921"},"modified":"2023-06-09T14:05:09","modified_gmt":"2023-06-09T08:35:09","slug":"kids-storage-organizer-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/kids-bedroom-interiors\/kids-storage-organizer-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"7 Clever Kids&#8217; Storage Organisers to Declutter Your Child&#8217;s Bedroom"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Organise your kid&#8217;s room like a pro with these 7 designer-recommended storage solutions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have kids, you know their room is an ever-messy space. How much ever you tidy it up, within seconds, it will become messy again. So, here are our 7 top organising kids&#8217; room storage ideas that will make your life much easier.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. Smart Kids&#8217; Storage Organiser<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With twins, cleaning and organising are like full-time jobs. No matter how much you invest in storage organisers, it&#8217;s never enough. So, the trick is to use the existing space in their room to create smart organisers. Take inspiration from the image below. We have used the high ceiling to our advantage and created a platform for building hidden storage spaces. The steps leading to the platform and the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/kids-bedroom-interiors\/bunk-bed-designs\/\">bunk beds<\/a> also have hidden drawers, so you never run out of storage space for their clothes, books, and toys.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134616\/smart-kids-storage-organizer.jpg\" alt=\"Kids organizer and storage bin for twin's room\" class=\"wp-image-46115\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134616\/smart-kids-storage-organizer.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134616\/smart-kids-storage-organizer-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134616\/smart-kids-storage-organizer-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134616\/smart-kids-storage-organizer-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Hidden kid&#8217;s toy organiser and storage bin for twin&#8217;s room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. Compact Storage Organiser For Kids&#8217; Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kids grow up very quickly. As a result, their needs and interests also shift rapidly. Hence, parents need to keep things simple and invest in furniture that is neutral in design and will last at least some years. This electric green and brown wardrobe is a sensible choice, with ample storage space and open shelves. And the best part, your child can reach even its top shelves easily.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134537\/compact-storage-organizer-for-kids-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Compact storage organizer with open shelves for kids bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-46109\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134537\/compact-storage-organizer-for-kids-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134537\/compact-storage-organizer-for-kids-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134537\/compact-storage-organizer-for-kids-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134537\/compact-storage-organizer-for-kids-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Kids room organisation storage for uncluttered space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Plan a fun kids bedroom design with our complete home interiors\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/07151624\/plan-fun-kids-bedroom-design-with-our-complete-home-interiors.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. Cupboard-style Kid&#8217;s Toy Organiser And Storage Bin<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Don&#8217;t have enough space for an additional toy organiser in your child&#8217;s space? Fret not. This modular cupboard can do the job of both clothes organiser and toy storage bin effortlessly. Plus, it comes with open shelves for special knick-knacks to display. The toy organiser below is made of clear fibreglass, so it&#8217;s not easily breakable, and your kid can select their favourite toy and reach it easily.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134543\/cupboard-style-kids-toy-organizer-and-storage-bin.jpg\" alt=\"Kid's toy organizer and storage bin in cupboard style\" class=\"wp-image-46110\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134543\/cupboard-style-kids-toy-organizer-and-storage-bin.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134543\/cupboard-style-kids-toy-organizer-and-storage-bin-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134543\/cupboard-style-kids-toy-organizer-and-storage-bin-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134543\/cupboard-style-kids-toy-organizer-and-storage-bin-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Kids storage organiser for compact space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">4. Modular Multifunctional Kid&#8217;s Bed-cum-Toy Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are struggling to tidy up and store your twin&#8217;s overflowing collection of toys, then it&#8217;s time to upgrade their room. This modular bunk bed with a staircase is an ideal choice. Wondering why? Because it comes with multiple hidden drawers in the form of steps of the staircase, and there are more drawers under the bottom bunk. Now that&#8217;s why we call space maximisation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134555\/kids-bed-cum-toy-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Kid's bed cum toy storage with staircase for twins\" class=\"wp-image-46112\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134555\/kids-bed-cum-toy-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134555\/kids-bed-cum-toy-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134555\/kids-bed-cum-toy-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134555\/kids-bed-cum-toy-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Kids toy organiser and storage bin natural with wooden finish<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">5. DIY Kid&#8217;s Storage Organiser: Shoe Cabinet-Turned-Bench<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We have converted a modular shoe cabinet into a bench for this bedroom. It is an interesting way to add storage and seating in a room with space constraints. Take a cue from the image below. The storage bench below the window keeps everything neat and uncluttered.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134610\/shoe-cabinet-turned-bench-for-kids.jpg\" alt=\"Converted modular shoe cabinet into a bench with storage for kids\" class=\"wp-image-46114\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134610\/shoe-cabinet-turned-bench-for-kids.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134610\/shoe-cabinet-turned-bench-for-kids-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134610\/shoe-cabinet-turned-bench-for-kids-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134610\/shoe-cabinet-turned-bench-for-kids-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Maximise space with a modular shoe cabinet turned storage bench for kids<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">6. Wooden Modular Multipurpose Bunk Bed With Attached Bookcase<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Create a fun and functional kid&#8217;s bedroom with a wooden modular bunk bed. The bottom bed is double size, the top bed is single size, and there is even a trundle bed for sleepovers. An attached staircase leads to the top bunk, and the side of the staircase doubles as a large bookshelf. The room features a wardrobe and a colour scheme of off-white and various shades of green.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134529\/bunk-bed-with-attached-bookcase-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Wooden bunk bed with a modular design and a conveniently attached book storage\" class=\"wp-image-46108\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134529\/bunk-bed-with-attached-bookcase-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134529\/bunk-bed-with-attached-bookcase-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134529\/bunk-bed-with-attached-bookcase-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134529\/bunk-bed-with-attached-bookcase-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Wooden modular bunk bed with clever storage space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">7. High-ceiling Kids&#8217; Bedroom With Dual Bunk Beds And Hidden Drawers<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Maximise storage space in a high-ceiling kid&#8217;s bedroom with dual bunk beds. Each bed comes with a study nook underneath and ample storage space. The beds are connected by a common set of stairs with hidden drawers at every step for additional storage. This design ensures your kids have room to decorate and customise to their heart&#8217;s content.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134549\/high-ceiling-kids-bedroom-with-dual-bunk-beds.jpg\" alt=\"High ceilings kids' bedroom features two bunk beds equipped with concealed drawers\" class=\"wp-image-46111\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134549\/high-ceiling-kids-bedroom-with-dual-bunk-beds.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134549\/high-ceiling-kids-bedroom-with-dual-bunk-beds-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134549\/high-ceiling-kids-bedroom-with-dual-bunk-beds-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/09134549\/high-ceiling-kids-bedroom-with-dual-bunk-beds-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Kids&#8217; dual bunk beds and hidden drawers<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In conclusion, keeping your kid&#8217;s room organised can be daunting, but with the right storage solutions, it can be made easy and stress-free. From smart storage organisers to modular multifunctional beds, there are many ways to maximise space in your little one&#8217;s room. If you want to customise your kid&#8217;s storage organiser, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">book an appointment<\/a> with our experts today and maximise space while minimising clutter. Check out our blog section for more tips on designing your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/kids-bedroom-interiors\/\">kid&#8217;s bedroom<\/a>!<\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Functional Interior Designs For You<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Speak to our interior experts today!<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option v